<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - The Daily Dairy</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .policy-section {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .policy-section h4 {
      color: #3B82F6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .policy-section ul {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .policy-icon {
      color: #3B82F6;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="container py-5" style="max-width:900px;">
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-primary text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    Your privacy matters. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information at <strong>The Daily Dairy</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h4><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-lock-fill policy-icon"></i> Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal data like name and email for account management</li>
      <li>Your contributions including posts, comments, and likes</li>
      <li>Device and log data such as IP address and browser type</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h4><i class="bi bi-gear-fill policy-icon"></i> How We Use Information</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Improve site functionality and user experience</li>
      <li>Communicate important updates with your consent</li>
      <li>Maintain security and prevent abuse</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-section">
    <h4><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill policy-icon"></i> Your Rights</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Access, update, or delete your personal data anytime</li>
      <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
      <li>Your data will never be sold to third parties</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="text-center">
    Questions? Please <a href="/contact" class="link-primary">contact us</a>.
  </p>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
